{"tid":626308,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩..真係好狗","createTime":"2018-04-12T04:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T05:29:17.000Z","uid":143372,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4c58c06f69a5719bef82280ce452059187188d31","tid":626308,"uid":143372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/121858_0eba7b45ea617630f755cd946d1cbcea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F121858_0eba7b45ea617630f755cd946d1cbcea.jpg&h=b6840baa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當巴塞全隊從羅馬連夜趕回巴塞隆拿的時候，已經是當地時間淩晨三點多了。他們會注意到，有一名球迷居然還在迎接他們回家。<br />\n<br />\n　　春寒料峭，天還下著雨，這位中年球迷身穿著巴塞的外套站在雨中，打一把透明的塑料傘。他雙手拿著標語，只能把傘柄搭在肩上，用頭撐住傘頂，右臂還掛著一個購物袋。標語上寫著：「恩尼斯達，別走；華維迪，別走。」左袖褲子都濕了。<br />\n<br />\n　　不知他從幾點開始等，終於等到球隊乘大巴回來。球員們進入停車場開出奧迪，各回各家。無論他們是否看到了這位球迷，經歷慘敗後也<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>沒有下車慰問</strong></span>。也許這名球迷在乎的也不是球員們的回應，而是真正能用自己的行動鼓勵到他們吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2ea473d09a46e4ed6befdcdfe82d35883ebddd","tid":626308,"uid":99403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"第一次同情疤狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e4f388f5c2e12922ee0ed80129accf08b55368","tid":626308,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:23:13.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪人情味囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聞唔聞到牙"},{"pid":"c90c70ada02a7dd6b487e5982de2e544579e30e3","tid":626308,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89a97b07775639094263569fe522ba413f845fd","tid":626308,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:31:58.000Z","msg":"土方蛇辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780279ed7b1c0d2b02146bdb105bc3c7608a4b30","tid":626308,"uid":86809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:15:48.000Z","msg":"連登疤迷淨係識打下口水戰得閒屈下人黑哨同輸波就怪乜怪物叫人out咋嘛<br />\n邊識依d架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad1ccdfc03b60a8a36d72a241da641f3715cd02","tid":626308,"uid":175032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a89a97b07775639094263569fe522ba413f845fd","tid":626308,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:31:58.000Z","msg":"土方蛇辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:29:17.000Z","msg":"土方蛇爆左血管唔係佢黎"}]}